Executive Summary 
 The hardware of information sytems consist of physical components of digital tech that you can touch

Information System Components

There are five information system componetents; Hardware, Software, Database, Network, and People. 
The hardware is the input and output, processor, operating system, and media devices. 
The software is the programs and procedures.The database is used for organizing data in a required structure. 
The Network consists of hubs, communication media, and network devices.

GitHub

GitHub is a git repository hosting system that includes its own features. 
GitHub is a code hosting platform for version control and collaboration. 
It lets you and others work together on projects from anywhere.

Client - Server Architecture

Client - server architecture is a computing model in which the server hosts,
delivers, and manages most of the resources and services to be used by the client.

Cloud Computing

the practice of using servers to store, manage, and process data, rather than a local server or a personal computer.
Many poeple use this so they dont need to use the same computer, 
and they can login in on a different computer and tell have the same files, photos and documents.

Conclusion

The configuration of a personal computer is extermely similar to any digital computing device.

